            </ul>
            <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-secondary">Get Started</a>
          </div>
          <div class="pricing-card featured reveal reveal-d2">
            <h3>Growth</h3>
            <div class="price">$5,000 <span>SGD/mo</span></div>
            <p class="pricing-desc">For businesses ready to dominate AI recommendations.</p>
            <ul class="pricing-features">
              <li>Everything in Essentials</li>
              <li>Content optimisation (20 pages/mo)</li>
              <li>Authority building &amp; directory work</li>
              <li>Bi-weekly reporting + competitor benchmarks</li>
              <li>Dedicated GEO strategist</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</a>
          </div>
          <div class="pricing-card reveal reveal-d3">
            <h3>Enterprise</h3>
            <div class="price">$10,000+ <span>SGD/mo</span></div>
            <p class="pricing-desc">Full-service AI search domination across all platforms.</p>
            <ul class="pricing-features">
              <li>Everything in Growth</li>
              <li>Multi-platform defensive monitoring</li>
              <li>Wikipedia presence strategy</li>
              <li>Custom prompt monitoring (50+ daily)</li>
              <li>Weekly strategy calls &amp; dashboard</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-secondary">Let's Talk</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ========== FAQ ========== -->
  <section class="section faq-section" id="faq" style="background: var(--bg-alt);" aria-label="Frequently asked questions about GEO agencies in Singapore">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header reveal">
        <p class="section-label">FAQ</p>
        <h2><span class="highlight">GEO Agency</span> — Questions <span class="highlight">Answered</span></h2>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-list">
        <details class="faq-item reveal reveal-d1" id="what-is-geo-and-how-is-it-different-from-seo">
          <summary>What is GEO and how is it different from SEO?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer"><p>GEO is Generative Engine Optimisation — getting your brand cited and recommended inside generative AI answers (ChatGPT, Gemini, Perplexity, Claude, Google AI Overviews). SEO targets the 10 blue links on a Google search page. GEO targets the AI-generated answer that increasingly appears above those links. Same business goal, different surfaces. Most GEO work overlaps with modern SEO (schema, content structure, authority) but the optimisation targets and measurement are different.</p></div>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item reveal reveal-d2" id="how-much-does-a-geo-agency-in-singapore-cost">
          <summary>How much does a GEO agency in Singapore cost?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer"><p>Our GEO plans start at S$3,000/month (Essentials), S$5,000/month (Growth), and S$10,000/month (Enterprise). The one-time AI Visibility Audit (AVA) sits below at S$1,000. SG GEO market pricing currently runs S$2,500–S$15,000/month depending on scope. Anything below S$2,000/month is almost certainly traditional SEO rebranded.</p></div>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item reveal reveal-d3" id="which-ai-platforms-does-a-geo-agency-optimise-for">
          <summary>Which AI platforms does a GEO agency optimise for?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer"><p>The five with meaningful SG traffic: ChatGPT (largest by user count), Google AI Overviews and Gemini, Perplexity (highest commercial intent), Claude (rising fast in B2B), and Microsoft Copilot. The technical layer — schema, llms.txt, content structure — applies across all five. Where they diverge is authority signals: Perplexity weighs citations heavily, ChatGPT favours Wikipedia, Gemini blends in Google Search ranking.</p></div>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item reveal reveal-d1" id="how-long-does-geo-take-to-show-results-in-singapore">
          <summary>How long does GEO take to show results in Singapore?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer"><p>Technical setup (schema, llms.txt, content restructure) ships in 2-4 weeks. First branded AI citations typically appear within 8-12 weeks. Category citations (e.g. ranking when someone asks "best clinic in Singapore" without your brand name) take 4-6 months and require ongoing authority work. SG-specific citation density takes slightly longer than global benchmarks because AI models lean US/UK.</p></div>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item reveal reveal-d2" id="do-i-still-need-traditional-seo-if-i-m-doing-geo">
          <summary>Do I still need traditional SEO if I'm doing GEO?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer"><p>Yes. Google still drives 60-70% of high-intent commercial search traffic in Singapore. GEO is additive, not a replacement. The work overlaps significantly though — schema, content structure, and authority signals serve both. If your Google rankings are weak we usually recommend a combined SEO + GEO engagement rather than GEO standalone.</p></div>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item reveal reveal-d3" id="can-you-guarantee-ai-overviews-citations">
          <summary>Can you guarantee AI Overviews citations?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer"><p>No. AI Overviews trigger probabilistically based on query type, user signal, and content authority. We can engineer the conditions that make citation likely — structured data, clear definitions, ranking inside Google's top 10 (the AI Overview pool draws primarily from top results). We report monthly on which of your tracked queries trigger AI Overviews and whether your brand appears. Most clients see first AI Overview citations within 6-10 weeks.</p></div>
        </details>
